---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<Base title="Application: AIOS" description="Raha Teimuri's application for Head of Viral Social at AIOS" active="work">
  <article class="app-page">
    <header class="app-head section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <a href="/#work" class="back">← All work</a>
        <h1 class="app-title">Application for Head of Viral Social (UGC & Clippers)</h1>
        <p class="app-sub">AIOS Medical</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="app-body section">
      <div class="wrap app-prose">
        <p class="app-greeting">To: Richie & the AIOS team</p>

        <p class="app-hook">
          I make brands go viral organically, and I turn it into revenue.
        </p>

        <p>
          I grew a travel brand from zero to 1M+ followers without ad spend, directed 50M+ views, and drove €80K/yr in tracked bookings (promo codes, UTM, GA4). Now I lead social for Yousician and GuitarTuna, where I've tripled content output, built our UGC and creator systems end-to-end, and use Claude and Superscale to ship more at volume.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your KPI is 40M organic branded views. I haven't done that in health content yet, which is harder than travel (compliance, sensitivity, semaglutide psychology aren't tailwinds). But the engine transfers: I know what hooks stop the scroll, what formats people share, how to turn one viral hit into a series. I build UGC pipelines, manage creators, run analytics loops, and test at speed.
        </p>

        <p>
          The team, the intensity, the mission to 100 million patients. That's why I'm here.
        </p>

        <div class="app-cta">
          <p class="app-sign">Raha</p>
          <a href="mailto:rahateimuri@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .app-page { min-height: 100vh; }
  .app-head { padding-top: 120px; }
  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .back:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .app-title { font-size: var(--t-h2); margin: 6px 0 16px; }
  .app-sub { font-size: var(--t-body-lg); color: var(--accent); margin: 0; }

  .app-body { padding-bottom: 80px; }
  .app-prose { max-width: 720px; }
  .app-prose p { font-size: var(--t-body-lg); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 20px; }
  .app-greeting {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .app-hook {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .app-cta { margin-top: 40px; }
  .app-sign { font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
</style>
